Dashboard Organization:

Main Dashboard Sections:
Dashboard Navigation:
├── 📊 Overview (current dashboard)
├── 👥 Employees (manage staff)
├── 📅 Schedule (create/edit schedules)
├── ⚙️ Settings (business configuration)
└── 📈 Reports (exports, analytics)

Settings Page Structure:
Option 1: Dedicated Settings Page
URL: /dashboard/settings

Settings Categories:
├── 🏢 Business Information
├── �� Business Hours
├── �� Roles & Positions
├── 💰 Pay & Billing
└── 🔔 Notifications

Recommended Approach: Settings Page
Why a Dedicated Page is Better:
✅ More space - Can show all options clearly
✅ Better organization - Group related settings together
✅ Easier navigation - Clear URL structure
✅ Mobile friendly - Works better on small screens
✅ Future expandable - Can add more settings later

Settings Page Layout:
Business Information Section:


┌─────────────────────────────────────┐
│ Business Information            [Edit] │
├─────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Business Name: Joe's Coffee Shop     │
│ Time Zone: Eastern Time (UTC-5)      │
│ Address: 123 Main St, City, State    │
│ Phone: (555) 123-4567                │
└─────────────────────────────────────┘


